posting_body: ['Available Date: Now', 'Apartment #: 110', 'Size:  1,266 sq ft | Noble Floor Plan', 'Best Rate: $3940 with a 15-month lease.', 'Pricing is subject to change daily.', '***Our offices are fully open.', 'We are currently offering both virtual (Realync), Guided, or Self-Guided tours.', '***', 'Welcome Home to The Kensington!', 'Refresh your senses each day in this boutique-style garden oasis with lush landscaping, rich architectural motifs, and stunning views of Pleasanton Ridge.', 'This sunny and spacious 1st floor Noble Floor Plan is waiting for you.', 'The Noble floor plan offers you 1,266sq.', 'ft. of living space, 2 Bedroom, 2 Bathroom-Granite kitchen countertops', '-Stainless steel appliances*', '-Wood plank flooring in the kitchen and bathrooms', '-Full-size, in-unit washer and dryer', '-Private patio', '-Central AC/Heat', 'We love your furry friends!', 'Pet’s welcome, additional deposit and pet rent apply.', 'Community Amenities Include:', '-Year-round heated swimming pool and spa', '-On-site maintenance', '-24-hour fitness center', '-PS4/XBox game room', '-Playground', '-Business center', '*Optional detached garages for an additional $60 per month', 'The Kensington is centrally located and makes commuting a breeze.', 'The 680 is about half a mile down the street and we are just a few miles from BART.', 'We also have great restaurants, CVS Pharmacy, Safeway, Hearst Elementary School, Alameda County Fairgrounds, and Patelco Sports Park within walking distance.', 'Downtown Pleasanton, which boasts a quaint Main St. with boutique shops, restaurants, breweries, and wine bars, is only a mile away.', 'Everything you need is right here!', 'You may view floor plans, schedule a tour, or reserve your next home on our website at:', '<URL>/', 'Call us today!', 'show contact info', 'Our Leasing Office is open 6 days a week:', 'Monday-Friday: 9:00 am - 6:00 pm', 'Saturday 10:00am - 5:00 pm', 'Directions:', 'I-680 -- Exit on Bernal Ave, turn East and head towards downtown', 'Make a right turn onto Valley Ave', 'You will see us almost immediately on your left-hand side.', 'There is a semi-circular driveway entrance and a large US Flag out front.', 'Please note pricing is subject to change daily.']
